Why we need wait methods
1. To avoid extra time in the script that we are using
2. If element got appeared in 1 sec then whole remaining time will be considered and wasted
3. Not good from scalability perspective


Type of wait
1. Hard wait- time.sleep(10)
2. Implicit wait -
3. Explicit wait -
4. Fluent wait -

Proper identification of test case by detailing in test case name
Use assertion in every test cases
